There are cracks in the wall, it seems to have been left alone for
many years.

There seems to be cracks in the wall, as if it has been left alone for
many years.
There is one crystal placed in each map
You can recover here, so it will be useful for dungeon conquest.

As I walked down the road, I saw the figures of two people in front of
me.
I apologize before the two of them can say anything.

It's not \n[1]'s fault for apologizing. We are the ones who should be
sorry for making you feel uncomfortable.

I felt relieved as I looked at the two of them, who always had a
gentle smile on their faces.

Hey... When we get back to \n[1] Village, there's something we want to
tell you.

I wonder what they want to talk about...? Of course, I'll respond with
an immediate I'm fine.

I apologize before the two of them can say anything.

It's not \n[1]'s fault for apologizing. We're the ones who should be

Hey... When we get back to \n[1] Village, there's something we want to
tell you.

I wonder what they want to talk about...? Of course, I'll respond with
an immediate I'm fine.
As I continued down the road, I saw Light's figure in front of me.
Thank goodness... It seems like Light is also safe.

If both of them were together, then there shouldn't be any problem if
\n[1] was there.

...The atmosphere is different from earlier, isn't it? Did something
happen, by any chance?

Well, it doesn't seem to be a bad thing. I may end up causing trouble
until the end, but I'm counting on you.
As I continued down the road, I saw Light ahead of me.
Thank goodness... It seems like Light is also safe.

If both of them were together, and \n[1] was there, then it seems like
there's no problem.

...The atmosphere is different from earlier. Did something happen, by
any chance?

Well, it doesn't seem like a bad thing. I might end up causing trouble
until the end, but I'm counting on you.
As I continued down the road, I saw Light ahead of me.
Thank goodness... It seems like Light is also safe.
It seems like everything is fine if \n[1] was there with Light.

...The atmosphere is different from earlier, isn't it? Could it be
that something happened?

Well, it doesn't seem to be a bad thing. I may end up causing trouble
until the end, but I'm counting on you.
Light's behavior seems strange. I wonder if something is wrong?
Ah, sorry for making you worry.

...I remembered something from the past, about myself before I met
\n[1].
It seems like I was the cause of this curse.
I'm always causing trouble for \n[1], I'm sorry...
There's no need to interrupt and speak with such hesitation.

Because Light is my best friend, there's no need for a reason to
support each other and be there for one another.
...That's right, I truly have a great best friend.

The demon I'm going to meet from now on is actually the person I have
feelings for.
I'll introduce you next time, I'm sure you two will get along well.

I was surprised to suddenly be enveloped in light... but, because
Light was there, I wasn't scared.
I was a little scared too, you know... Can I hold your hand?

Both of you! Isn't Light in trouble? Wasn't Light scared? I'll be by
his side, so don't worry.
